{"tid":2092553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義務律師：兩名涉違國安法人士被警方抽取DNA","createTime":"2020-07-03T09:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T10:23:27.000Z","uid":7542,"like":124,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":113,"replies":[{"pid":"c24d836569034bf9e5dfe896831f34eab3300f3f","tid":2092553,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"協助其中3名涉嫌違反《港區國安法》被捕人士的義務律師彭皓昕表示，當日到警署協助他們時，起初警方都不清楚是否可以讓被捕者保釋，形容處理過程存在不確定性，令被捕人士和他們的家人都感到好擔心。她又說，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">其中兩名被捕者，被警方抽取DNA樣本，她曾經向警員了解原因，有警員向她表示，因被捕人士干犯的是嚴重罪行，如果有任何不滿，可提出司法覆核。</span></strong>彭皓昕表示，警方的確有權抽取DNA樣本，但過去一般都是涉及一些打鬥或強姦的案件，希望透過樣本，證明被捕人曾接觸一些人或物件。<br />\n<br />\n但她認為今次涉及港區國安法的案件，警方根本無需透過DNA，以證明他們藏有涉嫌違法的物品，因此抽取樣本是無必要及不合比例。彭皓昕表示，在整個過程中，她認為被捕人士都享有與其他案件般的法律權利，最起碼可以與律師見面，亦可行使緘默權。警方7月1日拘捕10人，涉嫌違反《港區國安法》，其中9人獲准保釋，其餘1人被控一項煽動他人分裂國家罪及一項恐怖活動罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535640-20200703.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535640-20200703.htm&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=bc266a94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535640-20200703.htm&h=b67e34c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535640-20200703.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>題外話，當年東德秘密警察會抽取每個人嘅氣味樣本</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXL7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=7d3579fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a>"},{"pid":"445bc0b2f1c918bc06001cc7972d6f611ab07172","tid":2092553,"uid":68689,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"證明被捕人曾接觸一些人或物件定係被接觸一些人或物件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4f5078267acc068e9ed9a56e1bd9b6567edd91","tid":2092553,"uid":26770,"like":263,"dislike":4,"score":259,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">荃灣警局輪姦案又唔見抽驗</span>"},{"pid":"7d9719f7d73c15f9e763118683ec3c5cafb03005","tid":2092553,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"手套啊"},{"pid":"85ce99820f731bcd75e21b320b5fabc974f35a4a","tid":2092553,"uid":45910,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"DNA database<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d199d970393c1ae0e859b598978edce2a5247e2","tid":2092553,"uid":183509,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"中國好似所有被捕人都要抽，<br />\n而家match返個做法。"},{"pid":"f49e627831acfec739f27e83a4ef99fe8955540c","tid":2092553,"uid":51583,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"9人保釋<br />\n咁佢地走唔走好"},{"pid":"27a4080d981108315701887e514d2b074ee49ab1","tid":2092553,"uid":25424,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後入左中共DNA資料庫"},{"pid":"4ea421a63e79e9a73baf32294490d8a46209702e","tid":2092553,"uid":121197,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6e4f5078267acc068e9ed9a56e1bd9b6567edd91","tid":2092553,"uid":26770,"like":263,"dislike":4,"score":259,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">荃灣警局輪姦案又唔見抽驗</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"其實有抽<br />\n不過之後告番受害人咁解"},{"pid":"30223e14e96479979b6874c5c8361e3ac99523c7","tid":2092553,"uid":83251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"大陸<img src=\"/assets/f